  <p><strong>Mission</strong></p>
  <p>Flourish is a project aiming to make it easier for everyone to support each other.</p>
  <p><strong>Flourishites</strong></p>
  <p>The project is supported by its <%= @active_member_count %> members and its <%= link_to 'lone web developer and admin', "https://www.linkedin.com/in/luke-cassar-17885a29/", target: "_blank" %>.</p>
