  <p>The project is open source, and issues can be raises and discussed on our <%= link_to 'GitHub page', "https://github.com/cassar/flourish", target: "_blank" %></a>.</p>
  <p><strong>Get in Contact</strong></p>
  <p>If you are interested in helping Flourish grow, we'd love to hear from you at the below.</p>
  <p><i>Email:</i> <span data-cooperative-target="email"></span></p>
