  <p>If you would like to keep up to date with the project, simply <%= link_to 'sign up', new_user_registration_path %>, members receive a, 'Distribution Preview', email every <%= DistributionPreviewDateService::DAY_OF_THE_WEEK %> which has the latest Flourish news.</p>
